    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">
      <b>Effective date:</b> 7 July 2026<br>
      <b>Publisher:</b> Florence Publishing Ltd (trading as niallcodes)
    </p>
    <div class="tldr">
      <h2>The short version</h2>
      <p>PeekPic is local-only by design. It has no accounts, no analytics, no telemetry, no tracking, and no server of its own. It never sends your page content, browsing history, or any behavioural data anywhere — there's nowhere to send it.</p>
    </div>
